    "Free-to-paid conversion doubled",
    "We predict the redesign will generate approximately €180,000 in revenue in 2025",
  ],
  operationalEfficiencyItems: [
    "Over 20 redesigned views and 4 completely new views",
    "New purchase paths, brand refresh, and websites",
    "Invoice creation and sending speed increased by 30%"
