        "Additionally, a competitor analysis was conducted to identify Nettilasku\'s strengths and areas for development in the market. This provided valuable information for enhancing usability and customer experience. Business objectives, such as product profitability and customer relationship sustainability, were integrated into the development work to make the service both attractive and financially sound."
      ]
    },
    {
      title: "Design Process and Implementation",
      content: [
        "The visual refresh in Autumn 2024 gave the service a modern look and improved its functionality. This facelift laid the foundation for continuous UI/UX development. Navigation and visual guidance were enhanced by adding clear elements, such as arrows and animations, making it easier to find important functions.",
        "To clarify navigation, active tabs were emphasized, and scrolling functionalities were improved. Communication was enhanced by clarifying messages and notifications both visually and structurally, making them more understandable and easily accessible.",
        "Revamping the access rights logic enabled the management of multiple company accounts with a single user profile, offering users flexibility and ease. Additionally, product package pricing was reviewed to attract broader user groups.",
        "During the project, regular weekly meetings and active communication on instant messaging platforms kept all parties updated on development progress. Appointing a UI/UX specialist and the development work led by Tuomas Kaartoluoma clarified responsibilities and brought consistency to the work."
      ]
    },
    {
      title: "Results and Impacts",
      content: [
        "The project resulted in a modernized and more user-friendly solution that better meets user needs and enables expansion into international markets.",
        "The user interface was clarified and its navigation improved, making the service more intuitive and increasing user satisfaction. More flexible access rights logic allows managing data for different companies from a single user account, which simplifies users\' work and saves time.",
        "Weekly recurring revenue (ARR) increased by 55%, media budget ROI grew by 622%, and average customer MRR rose by 46%. Customer satisfaction also improved significantly, reflected in a 25% increase in customer loyalty."
      ]
    },
    {
      title: "Project Scope and Achievements",
      content: [
        "During the project, over 20 redesigned views were implemented, such as sales and purchase invoice creation, as well as four completely new views: homepage, your orders, service provider tendering, and private messaging.",
