---

<BaseLayout 
  title={pageTitle} 
  description={description}
  ogImage="/images/eemel/eemel_hero.webp"
>
  
  <HeroSection
      title="Eemel.com Redesign & Brand Refresh"
      paragraph="Eemel.com (formerly Nettilasku.fi) is a comprehensive financial management solution for small businesses. Aiming for international markets, the company needed a radical renewal."
      primaryButtonText="See results →"
      linkToResults={true}
      secondaryButtonText="Read the full story"
      secondaryButtonHref="#full-story-section"
      imageUrl="/images/eemel/eemel_hero.webp"
      imageAlt="Eemel.com case study hero image"
      paddingBottom="4rem"
  />

  <article class="case-study">

    <header class="case-study-header">
      {/* Removed the h1 from here as it\'s now in the hero section */}
    </header>

    <CaseStudySection id="initial-situation-heading" title="Eemel.com Initial Situation">
      <p>Eemel.com, formerly Nettilasku.fi, is a financial management software for small businesses, established in 2010. The service provides tools for invoicing, payroll, time tracking, and automated accounting. The company aimed for international markets with the renewed Eemel.com brand.</p>
      
      <p>The outdated user interface had become an obstacle to growth. Poor user experience reduced customer loyalty and lowered conversion rates. Users often switched to competing solutions.</p>
      
      <div class="quote-in-section">
        <img src="/images/eemel/jarkko_kahkonen_eemel.webp" alt="Jarkko Kähkönen" class="quote-image" />
        <p class="quote-text">"Using the media budget was no longer profitable, and product-led growth units were not functioning. Our user interface did not meet the expectations of modern users, and we desperately needed a strategic renewal." - Jarkko Kähkönen, Entrepreneur, Eemel.com</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>Aggressive pricing and free trials from competitors posed an additional challenge. It was clear that the current user experience did not support growth targets, so something had to be done.</p>
    </CaseStudySection>

    <ResultsSection 
      title={resultsData.title}
      subtitle={resultsData.subtitle}
      metricCards={resultsData.metricCards}
      businessGrowthTitle="Business Benefits"
      businessGrowthItems={resultsData.businessGrowthItems}
      operationalEfficiencyTitle="Implemented during the project"
      operationalEfficiencyItems={resultsData.operationalEfficiencyItems}
    />

    <div class="full-width-section">
      <ComparisonSliderSection dragIndicatorText="Drag me" />
    </div>

    <div id="full-story-section">
      <FullStorySection 
        title={fullStoryData.title}
        introduction={fullStoryData.introduction}
        sections={fullStoryData.sections}
        readMoreText="Read full story"
        showLessText="Show less"
      />
    </div>
    
    <div class="full-width-section">
      <CTASection
        title="Ready to grow fast?"
        paragraph="Let's discuss how our design expertise can help your SaaS company achieve its growth potential."
        formTitle="Leave your contact information, and we'll be in touch."
      />
    </div>

  </article>

  <TestimonialSection 
    customerName="Jarkko Kähkönen"
    customerTitle="Founder & CEO"
    customerCompany="Eemel.com"
    testimonialText="The employees of The Goodside handled the task brilliantly, and the outcome of the UX design work was excellent. Everything was done on schedule, as agreed, and in an honest and straightforward manner."
    customerImage="/images/eemel/jarkko_kahkonen_eemel.webp"
  />

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .gradient-heading-lg {
    /* Override global style to match contact page h1 */
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  }

  .case-study {
    max-width: 80ch; /* Limit line length for readability */
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .case-study-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--neutral-light);
  }

  .case-study-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xxl);
  }

  .case-study-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .sub-section {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .sub-section h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg); /* Adjust subheading size */
    color: var(--neutral-dark);
  }

  .bullet-list,
  .numbered-list {
    list-style-position: outside;
    padding-left: var(--spacing-lg); /* Indent list items */
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .bullet-list li,
  .numbered-list li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    line-height: var(--line-height-loose);
  }

  .results-list strong {
      color: var(--success-color); /* Highlight positive results */
  }

  .client-quote {
    margin: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    background-color: var(--neutral-lightest);
    border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  }

  .client-quote.with-image {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; /* Image takes its width, text fills rest */
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .client-quote blockquote {
    margin: 0;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--neutral-darker);
  }

  .client-quote cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    color: var(--neutral-dark);
  }

  .quote-image {
    width: 120px; /* Adjust image size */
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 0; /* Make image square */
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .case-study-figure {
    margin: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .case-study-image {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  figcaption {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--neutral-medium);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Basic responsiveness */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .client-quote.with-image {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Stack image and text on smaller screens */
      text-align: left;
    }

    .quote-image {
      margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-md); /* Left-align image when stacked */
    }
  }

  /* Make comparison slider take full width */
  .full-width-section {
    width: 100vw;
    position: relative;
    left: 50%;
    right: 50%;
    margin-left: -50vw;
    margin-right: -50vw;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  /* --- REMOVED HERO-TYYLIT --- */
  /* .hero-grid { ... } */
  /* .hero-content .hero__title { ... } */
  /* .hero-buttons { ... } */
  /* .hero-buttons .btn { ... } */
  /* .hero-buttons .btn:not(.btn--primary) { ... } */
  /* .hero-buttons .btn:not(.btn--primary):hover { ... } */
  /* @media (max-width: 992px) { ... } */
  /* --- LOPPU POISTETUT HERO-TYYLIT --- */

</style> 